divs: Sighting DetailsI stepped outside and looked up to see a white cigar-shaped UFO heading East over Moose Jaw. It didn't appear to have any wings or trails. I've included a few cropped screenshots of a few frames from the video recording of the event. I wish to retain the video recording from MUFON because it would end up on the public domain. There were a few witnesses I will not be including on the MUFON report form. If MUFON wishes to have a copy of the video recording, contact me via the email provided on my report form, so long as the video is not made out publicly. I will add also that during the night I was watching the sky to see star-like objects heading North. They did the usual... See my previous reports for details. Thank you
Summary: Cigar-shaped UFO over Moose Jaw, Saskatchewan
